properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued February 9 at 6:39PM PST until February 10 at 3:00AM PST by NWS San Francisco CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...North winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to 30 kt and
rough waters expected.

* WHERE...San Pablo Bay, Suisun Bay, the West Delta and the San
Francisco Bay north of the Bay Bridge.

* WHEN...Until 3 AM PST Monday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 3 AM PST MONDAY... ...GALE WARNING WILL EXPIRE AT 7 PM PST THIS EVENING
